{"page_id": 32909, "slug": "Eva_Fan_Club", "title": "Eva Fan Club", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Eva Fan Club</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "[[File:EvaFanClubComicDan.png|thumb|Evangelion fan comic translated by [[Dan Kanemitsu]]. Full issue available [http://imgur.com/a/ChEDhEd here.]|260px]]\n\n'''Eva Fan Club''' (エヴァ友の会, ''Eva Tomo no Kai'') are a series of newsletters that were released with the original video and laserdisc release of ''Neon Genesis Evangelion'' in Japan. The limited Renewal DVD Box-set was packaged with a full set of reprints. \n\n{{stub}}\n\n{{Pub List}}\n\n[[Category:A to Z]]\n[[Category:Publications]]", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><figure typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:EvaFanClubComicDan.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/1/18/EvaFanClubComicDan.png/260px-EvaFanClubComicDan.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"260\" height=\"78\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/18/EvaFanClubComicDan.png/390px-EvaFanClubComicDan.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/18/EvaFanClubComicDan.png/520px-EvaFanClubComicDan.png 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Evangelion fan comic translated by <a href=\"/Dan_Kanemitsu\" title=\"Dan Kanemitsu\">Dan Kanemitsu</a>. Full issue available <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://imgur.com/a/ChEDhEd\">here.</a></figcaption></figure>\n<p><b>Eva Fan Club</b> (エヴァ友の会, <i>Eva Tomo no Kai</i>) are a series of newsletters that were released with the original video and laserdisc release of <i>Neon Genesis Evangelion</i> in Japan. The limited Renewal DVD Box-set was packaged with a full set of reprints. \n</p><p><br clear=\"all\" />\n<i>This article bears the unpleasant designation of \"<b>Stub</b>.\" This is a <b>Bad Thing</b>. Provide a great service to NGE fan-geeks everywhere by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://wiki.evageeks.org/index.php?title=Eva_Fan_Club&amp;actio